---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const pageTitle = "Melinda Canny";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
    <div class="gif">
        <img width="200" alt="Melinda Canny image" src="/melinda_author_photo.JPG"  />
    </div>
    <h1>Melinda Canny</h1>
    <small>Author</small>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
        Melinda Canny, a world traveler, Army Veteran, photographer,
        published poet, and lifelong storyteller, delves into the Ashwind
        series, a captivating tale following a group of magically gifted
        children striving to unite and safeguard their realm. Amidst their
        journey, some confront discrimination based on their disabilities or
        race, while others grapple with fear surrounding their unique abilities.
        
    </p>
    <p>
        Inspired by her own experiences, Melinda witnessed the impact of
        societal attitudes toward children with disabilities, particularly her
        son's journey through Special Ed, where he defied expectations and
        succeeded in all endeavors. Her advocacy centers on empowering children
        with disabilities, affirming their inherent value and boundless
        potential, echoing the message that they are capable of achieving
        anything they set their minds to.
    </p>

    <div class="button">
        <a href="/works/">
            <button class="button">My portfolio</button>
        </a>
    </div>
